data.description: Back on the Market due to Buyers Financing fell through to NO fault of the sellers. TOTAL RENOVATION FROM THE STUDS OUT!!! Don't miss out on this Beautiful 3 bed 2 bath 1951 cottage that is nestled on just under 1 acre. With such an extensive renovation this is practically a new home offering Granite Counters ~Stainless Steel Appliances ~ All new foundation ~ New HVAC ~ New Plumbing ~ New Electrical ~ Primary Bedroom has Vaulted Ceilings ~ Primary bath has tiled shower and Soaking Tub~ Additional room for office space ~ All new Flooring including subfloors ~ Covered front porch with 2 additional porches on each side of the home ~ Matching storage shed to remain ~ Property has a running creek on one side and the back of property. THIS IS A RENOVATION FOR THE BOOKS SO COME SEE IT TODAY!!!!
